---
import BaseLayout from '~/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Button from '~/components/Button.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="找不到頁面" description="您要造訪的頁面不存在。" noindex>
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-2xl px-4 py-24 lg:py-32 text-center">
    <p class="font-handwriting text-4xl text-espresso">404</p>
    <h1 class="mt-4 font-serif text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-charcoal">
      頁面找不到了
    </h1>
    <p class="mt-4 text-charcoal/80">
      您造訪的網址可能已搬移或不存在。回首頁看看，或從導覽列重新瀏覽。
    </p>
    <div class="mt-8 flex justify-center gap-4">
      <Button href="/" variant="primary" size="md">回首頁</Button>
      <Button href="/contact" variant="secondary" size="md">聯絡我們</Button>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
